ProductName: Nike SQ MachSpeed Iron Set 4-AW Steel Right Hand
ProductDescription: SQ Technology packed into a refined profile. The ultimate combination of built-in forgiveness with a hotter impact zone, Nike PowerBow weighting, and forged carbon steel body to deliver performance, feel and maximum distance.
BulletPoint1: A radical new construction method combined with a hot, thin alloy face creates the fastest Nike iron ever. Faster ball speeds off the face means more distance.
BulletPoint2: The combination of AM355 stainless alloy and an off-the-face weld construction creates a thinner, hotter face and wider sweet zone. This new construction offers an extremely hot center area, but also expands to lower on the face where the ball is more to be in contact.
BulletPoint3: The Nike PowerBow creates extreme deep CG. This provides a wider sweet spot and higher trajectory.
BulletPoint4: The deep undercut repositions 50 grams of weight low and back to the Nike PowerBow for high launching shots that travel far and land softly.

ProductDescription: The Nike Victory Red Pro Blade Iron Set is designed for golfers who want tour-level shot-shaping ability; precision, feel and consistency; and players wanting to out-play and out-perform competition.
BulletPoint1: Precision ball flight: The new X3X high-frequency groove process creates Nike's most exact iron faces ever. The new VR Pro blade has more groove, closer together and deeper, to ensure control and consistency. This new design conforms to new USGA and RA rules.
BulletPoint2: Crafted for consistency: Precision-forging to a near finished level eliminates most handwork and ensures consitency throughout the set. First each iron face is milled to a perfectly flat surface. The face is then carefully die-stamped, pressing grooves to exact specifications for extremely low variance and shot-making consistency.
BulletPoint3: Tour-ready control: The flatback design is the choice of top-level players seeking fell and shot-making workability.
